title: Kylie Jenner gets her leg hairs lasered off
text:
To say she's a fan of high-touch beauty procedures would be no secret.

And Kylie Jenner maintained her commitment to luxury upkeep on Saturday as she Insta-storied a video of herself getting her leg hairs lasered off at SEV Laser Aesthetics in LA.

The 22-year-old reality star captioned the video: 'afternoons at @sevlaseraesthetics.'

Busy: Kylie kept up her commitment to luxury upkeep on Saturday as she Insta-storied a video of herself getting her leg hairs lasered off at SEV Laser Aesthetics in LA

Kylie laid on a chair while the laser aesthetician ran a green light across her legs.

Her video comes a day after Kylie admitted she's 'accepted' her stretch marks during a question and answer series she set up through Instagram's 'ask me anything' feature on Friday night.

Kylie shares one-year-old daughter Stormi with rapper Travis Scott.

Getting real: Her video comes a day after Kylie admitted she's 'accepted' her stretch marks during a question and answer series she set up through Instagram's 'ask me anything' feature on Friday night

A fan asked if the Keeping Up With The Kardashians star had any stretch marks from being pregnant and what she used for treatment.

'On my breasts, butt and thighs,' she wrote. 'I haven't gotten rid of them ... just accepted them as a little gift from Stormi.'

Sticking to the pregnancy theme, she told her followers that there was 'nothing more special than feeling your baby move and grow' while she was pregnant.

Family: Kylie shares one-year-old daughter Stormi with rapper Travis Scott

Although she recently parted ways from Stormi's dad, Kylie still sees more children in her future.

'I can't wait to have more babies, but not ready just yet,' she wrote.

Travis and Kylie started dating in 2017 shortly after she split from rapper Tyga.
